room_title: Escape room "20,000 Leagues Under the Sea" by Mystery Escape Room Tucson in Tucson
room_description: Ah travelers! Welcome to your journey, 20,000 Leagues Under the Sea. You are about to move into a deep and unexplained world where few have dared venture! The profound ocean is filled with grotesque creatures, adventure, and a machine-like vessel that can dive deeper than the blue whale. This, the Nautilus Submarine of Captain Nemo, is your destination and you will embark on your voyage aboard this fantastic machine.
